# direnv configuration for llm-devcontainer project
#
# This file enables automatic environment loading when entering the directory.
# Run `direnv allow` to enable.

# Use the flake's devShell for native development
use flake

# Optional: Print reminder about container development
echo ""
echo "Native devShell loaded. For containerized development:"
echo "  nix run .#dev     # Interactive shell"
echo "  nix run .#claude  # Claude Code"
echo ""
